  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the component swizzle mapping for a Vulkan YCbCr conversion.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`GRVkYcbcrComponents` describes how the R, G, B, and A components are mapped when sampling a YCbCr texture through a Vulkan sampler YCbCr conversion. Each property accepts a Vulkan component swizzle value (e.g., `VK_COMPONENT_SWIZZLE_IDENTITY` = 0).

This struct is used as part of <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.GrVkYcbcrConversionInfo" /> when creating GPU surfaces backed by YCbCr textures.

## Examples

```csharp
var components = new GRVkYcbcrComponents
{
    R = 0, // VK_COMPONENT_SWIZZLE_IDENTITY
    G = 0,
    B = 0,
    A = 0,
};
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
